[SN]TITLE[SN]
NI Audit Office criticises councils over conflict policies

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A number of the new councils have been criticised by the NI Audit Office for not having conflict of interest policies in place after they were given responsibility for planning decisions.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
